[04:06.33] [Enter ORLANDO, with his sword drawn]
[04:06.96]ORLANDO Forbear, and eat no more.
[04:08.51]JAQUES Why, I have eat none yet.
[04:10.18]ORLANDO Nor shalt not, till necessity be served.
